 e is anything we can do to accomodate you.\nCalling to Wrestlers and Oil F
 airies !\napply at woofwoofgrrrl@proton.me\nWhat to send:\n-Your wrestler 
 name\n-Your pronouns\n-(for wrestlers) What kind of wrestling you wanna do
  (more salacious or more vicious)\n-If you have any particular needs/accom
 odation (idk if I can find you a costume but you could always ask)\n-Hones
 tly I'm kinda hesitant on a photo ? it feels weird to ask for a photo of s
 trangers so don't worry abt that\nhttps://woof-woof-grrrl.neocities.org/
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.openstreetmap.org/node/12034322502
